node.text: Keeping it real on the set of Samaritan... This is like it was many years ago when you use real locations, real buildings, real railroads, Real rain , and definitely real COLD! All credit to the director and the tough crew who makes my job easier than I deserve!
My daughter @sistinestallone Visiting me on the set of my new film SAMARITAN  after I had to take care of business! #Samaritan
@scarletstallone Hitting it dead center perfect! … I am jealous.
Happy Valentine’s Day to all my wonderful girls!
Sometimes this is how brothers communicate best!
Working away on MGM ‘s new  film Samaritan ... It’s Looking great.
Life imitating art during the visit to the art museum... What’s on her mind?

Man, I had the best fried chicken on the planet at a place called the BUSY BEE café , been there since 1946,in  Atlanta Georgia… Old school! I hung out with the very interesting customers who were lot of fun and loved Movies! I’ll be back , To quote a friend of mine
Starting with breakfast our favorite meal of the day. I’m starving since we hit the gym for about an hour and a half! #slystalloneshop @slystalloneshop
KIRK DOUGLAS!!! The last great giant of my cinema heroes has passed on to Infinite glory. Amazing artist... the likes of which we will never ever see again!
Images from the next Adventures of the EXPENDABLES - GO TO HELL!! … Thank you Chuck Dixon and your amazing team for working on this. Go out and get the graphic comic which is going to drop soon
Check it out on the “bloody disgusting” website and tell me what you think of this idea for A MOVIE! Thank you Chuck Dixon and your amazing work.
One way to stay in shape is to put your dessert on your face instead of in your stomach...
Thanks to @officialduffmckagan, my brilliant friend, and super badass bassist for the incredible @gunsnroses! NICE SHIRT, it reminds me of someone I used to know! @slystalloneshop

3 Days to Rock. Can’t wait for you guys to see what I’ve been up to with Facebook Groups. It’s hitting screens on 02.02.20. Stay tuned.
#sponsored #GetReadyToRock #MoreTogether

Sometimes I wake up I feel like doing nothing. Just relaxing. Just very true. If anyone says different, they’re lying - it’s human nature. 
Then you roll over, get a little mad at yourself, and realize to get anywhere you’ve got to make a deposit in the GOAL BANK. So, I’ll go back to my favorite phrase and do it!! #KeepPunching
The world lost a great man and a great champion. I feel so bad for his family. Breaks my heart. Athlete, writer, innovator, role model, #OneOfAKind.
What do you think @dollyparton?
At dinner with the incredible genius producer, Norman Lear, who changed the face of television years ago — a real pioneer! Look how he wants to knock me cold! #KeepPunching
It’s not safe anywhere especially when @sistinestallone is dressed up like a banana and is deadly with a BOW AND ARROW!!!!
Getting ready to head to location to start filming my next movie called SAMARITAN, so I’m enjoying a stroll with my wonderful daughter @sophiastallone
It’s always humbling to be in great company! P.S .Still can do it ...

The meeting of the masters. The Great #AlPacino meets the great @guyfieri!!! I really respect these guys. And a special shout out to a great man’s man @jayglazer who is hiding in the background, but brought us all together!
